channel.title: Making an RSPS
channel.description:
I don't want to leech, I want to make my own, from scratch... I looked for a guide but couldn't find one... I am pretty good at Java (Better than the average leecher) And I was just hoping for someone to help me, or point me in the right direction for help... If someone on these forums doesn't feel like being an asshole, my skype is Scyth3.pb
Thanks.

item.title: Making an RSPS
item.dc:creator: @Scyth1 Scyth_
item.description:
@Scyth1 wrote:

mgl:

I don’t think there’s a guide for coding on from “scratch”, if there was it would be awfully long… Anyways, why don’t you try a blank base. Like delta, hyperion or something like that. That way you can put your own spin on your server, its basically starting from scratch, just not all the way from scratch

Ill probably just get a delta and strip it of EVERYTHING and redo it
